HEADWORD: Hisingerite
<hw>His"ing*er*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Named after W.
<ets>Hisinger</ets>, a Swedish mineralogist.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
